37   Memory Channel
38   IPMI Device
39   Power Supply



查看服务器型号
dmidecode | grep "Product Name"

查看主板序列号
dmidecode | grep "Serial Number"

查看系统序列号
dmidecode -s system-serial-number

查看OEM信息
dmidecode -t 11



